structure.unit: PHYSICIANS, OSTEOPATHS, PODIATRISTS, AND RELATED MEDICAL PRACTITIONERS

law.text: If any section of this chapter or any part of any section shall be invalid or unconstitutional, the declaration of such invalidity shall not affect the validity of the remaining portions thereof.
